OL,6,GBBC News has confirmed a package of
OL,7,Gchanges to its services as it seeks
OL,8,Gto make millions of pounds in savings
OL,9,Gand shift resources online.
OL,11,FThe package confirms a number of
OL,12,Fmeasures that were leaked to media
OL,13,Foutlets back in October, when the
OL,14,Fplans were originally expected to be
OL,15,Fannounced.
