OL,3,CBBC confirms changes to BBC News
OL,4,Coutput in the coming year
OL,6,FCertainly, changes made to the BBC
OL,7,FNews Channel in the past two years,
OL,8,Fsteadily reducing UK content in
OL,9,Fadvance of this spring's merger with
OL,10,FBBC World News have driven audiences
OL,11,Faway. Back in May, Deadline reported
OL,12,Fhow the BBC News Channel had lost 1
OL,13,Fmillion viewers.
OL,15,FA fall in audiences can thus be used
OL,16,Fas an excuse to cut further. Online
OL,17,Fblogs are relatively cheap, compared
OL,18,Fto the running of a fully fledged
OL,19,Fnews service.
