OL,3,CBBC confirms changes to BBC News
OL,4,Coutput in the coming year
OL,6,FAnd the UK opt-out of the news
OL,7,Fchannel, streamed on the iPlayer is
OL,8,Foften a raw feed of an event,
OL,9,Fbroadcast for hours on end without
OL,10,Fmuch editorial comment, analysis or
OL,11,Finterviews.
OL,13,FWhen BBC News carries Parliamentary
OL,14,Fcoverage, the BBC News Channel is
OL,15,Feffectively simulcasting the same raw
OL,16,Ffeed as BBC Parliament, but with
OL,17,Fdifferent graphics.
