OL,3,CBBC confirms changes to BBC News
OL,4,Coutput in the coming year
OL,6,FThat a shift online does not
OL,7,Fnecessarily mean that viewers don't
OL,8,Fwant linear news is proved by the
OL,9,Fgrowth of streaming-only news
OL,10,Fchannels. NBC News Now is among those
OL,11,FUS channels originally designed as an
OL,12,Fonline-only service, although in the
OL,13,FUK NBC News Now does also have
OL,14,Fconventional broadcast outlets.
OL,16,FThe live nature of the news means
OL,17,Fviewers do want to dip in and out of
OL,18,Fnews coverage, even with set times
OL,19,Ffor headlines, but not necessarily on
OL,20,Fa normal TV screen anymore.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
