OL,3,CBBC confirms changes to BBC News
OL,4,Coutput in the coming year
OL,6,FOther broadcasters have invested in a
OL,7,Fstreaming-friendly news services that
OL,8,Fare also available where streamers
OL,9,Fare ` across various platforms and
OL,10,Fapps including YouTube. European
OL,11,Fexamples include Franceinfo.
OL,13,FThe BBC prefers to ring-fence its
OL,14,Fstreaming content on the iPlayer,
OL,15,Fwhich will limit the scope of its
OL,16,Fsuccess. Ofcom has previously noted
OL,17,Fhow the iPlayer actually isn't that
OL,18,Fbig in terms of its streaming rivals
OL,19,Fand how it fails to reach some
OL,20,Faudiences.
